.TH "ti_bandgap_build" 9 "ti_bandgap_build" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ti_bandgap_build \- parse DT and setup a struct ti_bandgap
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct ti_bandgap *" ti_bandgap_build
.BI "(struct platform_device *pdev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pdev" 12
pointer to device struct platform_device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Used to read the device tree properties accordingly to the bandgap
matching version. Based on bandgap version and its capabilities it
will build a struct ti_bandgap out of the required DT entries.
.SH "RETURN"
valid bandgap structure if successful, else returns ERR_PTR
return value must be verified with IS_ERR.
